        "creation_date": 1355257263,
        "body": "<p>The simple answer is that you should not treat textual data as a stream of bytes. Specifically that means: <strong>don't use <code>ByteBuffer<\/code><\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n<p>Use an <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/io/InputStreamReader.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>InputStreamReader<\/code><\/a>, which knows how to interpret sequences of bytes using a given encoding.<\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 13827867,
        "question_id": 13827809
    }],
